<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">December 14, 2007 | Page 6</font><P>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><B>VIEWS BELOW:</B><BR>
<A HREF="#Tabasco">Man-made disaster in Tabasco</A><BR>
